<p style='margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:107%;margin:0cm;'><span style='font-family:"Arial Black",sans-serif;color:#0E101A;'>The ongoing position of these green apparel in the market: -</span></p>
